API 接入与 OpenClaw 配置说明
请根据以下信息配置你的客户端。API Key 请替换为你自己的密钥。
API Base URL
统一接口地址
[v1](https://api.bjxrouter.com/v1)
OpenClaw 配置参考
将以下配置加入 OpenClaw 配置文件中，并替换 apiKey。
config.json
JSON
{
"models": {
"providers": {
"polaris": {
"baseUrl": "https://api.bjxrouter.com/v1",
"apiKey": "自己的api key",
"api": "openai-responses",
"headers": {
"User-Agent": "curl/8.0"
},
"authHeader": true,
"models": [
{
"id": "gpt-5.4",
"name": "gpt-5.4",
"reasoning": true,
"input": [
"text"
],
"cost": {
"input": 0,
"output": 0,
"cacheRead": 0,
"cacheWrite": 0
},
"contextWindow": 200000,
"maxTokens": 16000
}
]
}
}
},
"agents": {
"defaults": {
"model": {
"primary": "polaris/gpt-5.4"
}
}
}
}
退款政策
平台支持无理由退款，退款金额按实际充值与实际消费计算。
退款支持
支持无理由退款
退款计算公式
退款 = 实充金额 - 实消金额
示例：如果实充金额为 100 元，已实际消费 30 元，则可退款金额为 70 元。
请妥善保管自己的 API Key，避免泄露。

.notice-board{--bg:#ffffff;--panel:#f8fbff;--border:rgba(37,99,235,.12);--title:#0f172a;--text:#334155;--muted:#64748b;--accent:#2563eb;--accent-2:#06b6d4;max-width:920px;margin:24px auto;padding:32px;border-radius:28px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:radial-gradient(circle at top left,rgba(56,189,248,.16),transparent 28%),radial-gradient(circle at bottom right,rgba(99,102,241,.14),transparent 30%),var(--bg);box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(15,23,42,.08);overflow:hidden}
html.dark .notice-board{--bg:#0f172a;--panel:#111c34;--border:rgba(148,163,184,.14);--title:#e8eefc;--text:#cbd5e1;--muted:#94a3b8;--accent:#7dd3fc;--accent-2:#818cf8;box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(2,6,23,.45)}
.notice-eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(37,99,235,.12);color:var(--accent);font-size:12px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.12em}
html.dark .notice-eyebrow{background:rgba(125,211,252,.12)}
.notice-title{margin:18px 0 10px;font-size:44px;line-height:1.1;font-weight:900;color:var(--title)}
.notice-title span{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent-2),var(--accent));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
.notice-subtitle{margin:0 0 24px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.9;color:var(--text)}
.notice-list{display:grid;gap:16px}
.notice-row{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;padding:22px;border-radius:22px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,.10)}
html.dark .notice-row{background:rgba(15,23,42,.52);border-color:rgba(148,163,184,.08)}
.notice-num{width:44px;height:44px;flex:0 0 44px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent-2),#4f46e5)}
.notice-row-title{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:var(--title)}
.notice-row-text{margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.9;color:var(--text)}
.notice-row.notice-info{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(59,130,246,.10),rgba(14,165,233,.08)),rgba(255,255,255,.92);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.18);box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(59,130,246,.10)}
html.dark .notice-row.notice-info{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(96,165,250,.16),rgba(34,211,238,.10)),rgba(15,23,42,.68);border-color:rgba(96,165,250,.24);box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(96,165,250,.12)}
.notice-row.notice-info .notice-num{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#0ea5e9)}
.notice-row.notice-info .notice-row-title{font-size:21px;font-weight:900;color:#1d4ed8}
html.dark .notice-row.notice-info .notice-row-title{color:#93c5fd}
.notice-row.notice-info .notice-row-text{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.9;color:#1e3a8a}
html.dark .notice-row.notice-info .notice-row-text{color:#dbeafe}
.notice-row.notice-hot{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(239,68,68,.10),rgba(249,115,22,.08)),rgba(255,255,255,.92);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.18);box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(239,68,68,.10)}
html.dark .notice-row.notice-hot{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(248,113,113,.16),rgba(249,115,22,.10)),rgba(15,23,42,.68);border-color:rgba(248,113,113,.24);box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(248,113,113,.12)}
.notice-row.notice-hot .notice-num{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ef4444,#dc2626)}
.notice-row.notice-hot .notice-row-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:900;color:#dc2626}
html.dark .notice-row.notice-hot .notice-row-title{color:#fca5a5}
.notice-row.notice-hot .notice-row-text{font-size:18px;font-weight:800;line-height:1.95;color:#991b1b}
html.dark .notice-row.notice-hot .notice-row-text{color:#fee2e2}
.notice-link{color:var(--accent);font-weight:800;text-decoration:none}
.notice-link:hover{text-decoration:underline}
.notice-foot{margin-top:18px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}
@media (max-width:640px){.notice-board{padding:22px;border-radius:22px}.notice-title{font-size:32px}.notice-row{padding:18px}.notice-num{width:38px;height:38px;flex-basis:38px;font-size:18px}.notice-row.notice-hot .notice-row-title{font-size:20px}.notice-row.notice-hot .notice-row-text{font-size:16px}.notice-row.notice-info .notice-row-title{font-size:18px}.notice-row.notice-info .notice-row-text{font-size:15px}}
